    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">Outperforming steel utility blades and unquestionably sharper, these triangle replacement ceramic razor blades from ToolTreaux will likely have you making the permanent jump to ceramic. Why? Read on.<br><br>How many times do you have to replace dull or broken steel utility blades? Probably more than you think or like to admit. Compared to traditional metal blades, ToolTreaux’s ceramic box cutter blades will outperform standard steel blades, especially in a warehouse or commercial setting; that being said, they are totally suitable for at home, office or studio use for DIY projects or arts and crafts too</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n\n\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-repeat: repeat-x;\n\t\t\tborder-radius: 4px;\n\t\t\t-webkit-box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255,