em\">OUTPERFORM METAL BLADES: ToolTreaux’s ceramic zirconia triangle replacement utility knife blades will outperform standard steel or other metal blades, even in a warehouse or commercial setting; the ceramic box cutter blades will afford you a longer, more reliable and uninterrupted work flow across many different work or DIY projects</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">LONG LASTING BOX CUTTER BLADES: Durable, strong and always reliable, the ceramic zirconia construction allows for superior edge retention, long periods of incredible sharpness, and will slice through foam, paper, fabric, rubber and more with speed, accuracy and precision</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">CERAMIC ZIRCONIA REPLACEMENT BLADES: In this package you’ll receive 10 replacement utility knife ceramic razor blades; the razor blades are non dulling, rust resistant, nonmagnetic, nonmetallic and non porous, and come in a handy plastic storage case to keep unused blades secure</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">UTILITY KNIFE COMPATIBILITY: These ceramic triangle utility knife replacement blades measure 2 inches wide x 0.75 inch in length and are compatible with most standard utility knives and box cutters</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Case Dimensions: 5 x 2 x 0.06 inches; 10 Pack Weight: 0.05lbs; Color: White; Material: Ceramic Zirconia; Blade Weight: 0.01lbs; Blade Dimensions: 2 x 0.75 x 0.06 inches</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ToolTreaux White Ceramic Box Cutter Utility Knife Replacement Blades Craft Supplies, 10pk</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">34.95</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Outperforming steel utility blades and unquestionably sharper, these triangle replacement ceramic razor blades from ToolTreaux will likely have you making the permanent jump to ceramic. Why? Read on.\n\nHow many times do you have to replace dull or broken steel utility blades? Probably more than you think or like to admit. Compared to traditional metal blades, ToolTreaux’s ceramic box cutter blades will outperform standard steel blades, especially in a warehouse or commercial setting; that being said, they are totally suitable for at home, office or studio use for DIY projects or arts and crafts too. Regardless of place or project, this is what matters: these ceramic replacement utility blades will afford you a longer, more reliable and uninterrupted work flow across many different projects, saving you time, money and effort.\n\nWhat makes these replacement blades so unique? Their ceramic zirconia fabrication. Durable, strong and always reliable, the blades ceramic zirconia construction allows for long periods of incredible sharpness, non dulling superior edge retention, and will easily slice through foam, paper, fabric, rubber and more with speed, accuracy and precision. Notably, the box cutter blades are rust resistant, nonmagnetic, nonmetallic and non porous too, meaning not a lot is going to affect their performance or structural longevity.\n \nIn this package you’ll receive 10 replacement ceramic razor blades, secured in a handy plastic storage container to keep blades safe when not in use. These wear resistant, triangle replacement ceramic razor blades are compatible with most standard utility knives or box cutter knives.\n\nVery sharp, use with caution.\n\nSold as pack of 10.</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2024</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t&nbsp;<table></table>\n\t</div>\n\n <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"88\" height=\"33\" src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_poweredby-en.gif\"></a></center>",
